name: Dysfunctional Unicorn Nft Collection By Coops 02/08
description: Hey and welcome to the Dysfunctional Unicorn (DU) family! DU 02 is the middle triplet and she has quite the outgoing personality! She is a sweetie, but if you mess with her, you'll get the rainbow horn. DU 02 is proud of her glitchy liquified beauty, but, has always been jealous of her triplet DU 03 for being the most dysfunctional/beautiful of the three. She is an Augmented Reality image so she loves crashing any and all photo-opps. Copy and paste her on your instagram/snapchat story and  take her everywhere you go! You can see her as a DU, or you can see her as a horse with a glitched rainbow sword on her head made to protect you and all your hopes and dreams.
